#ok, so you have decided to use my code to cheer your colleagues on the daily basis
# disclaimer, this code is inspired by someone else's

To automate it work you can do it through "cronetab"
1. type in terminal with your code: "cronetab -e"
2. in the open cronfile type "* * * * * python path_to_the_folder_with_the_script/send_insiprations_over_mail.py". The * are responsible for the minutes, hours, etc.
3. check the crontab.guru website to make sure you understand what is the schedule for the script should be
4. run "service cron status" to check if it is running
5. run "service cron start" to start the cron schedule for the script
 
